content: I do not have access to the latest information on the nba rosters or stats. but as per the last conclusion in the nba 2018-2019 season, the golden state warriors' roster depth was considered one of the strongest in the western conference. they had multiple all-stars and experienced players on their roster, and also added depth through role players and rookies. however, the competitiveness of the western conference can fluctuate from season to season, so it is difficult to make a definitive comparison.
